  "text": "Thus, the Multi-Dilation (MD) module is developed, which is based on the MC features. The dilated convolution, which expands the context window size of the convolution without downsampling or convolving with larger filters of more parameters, is employed in the MD module. By combining multiple dilated convolutions [CITATION_1] with different rates and a global pooling, the MD module extracts crack features with multiple context sizes and detects cracks with different widths and topologies.",
